{"tid":2216070,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［鬥慘大會］分享下濕鳩肺炎搞到你有幾慘","createTime":"2020-09-24T11:47:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T11:58:41.000Z","uid":99778,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4720d2f182b1722e4ab73fd01006ae4783f3fb95","tid":2216070,"uid":99778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:47:45.000Z","msg":"濕鳩肺炎開始咗之後<br />\n工作即刻大受影響  <br />\n比佢搞到雞毛鴨血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一嚟無工開 二嚟人工低咗好多<br />\n講緊本身份人工都係$14000-15000<br />\n依家個個月都得$7000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身份工唔係咩好有前途嘅職業<br />\n但真係自己想做嘅工 好撚有熱誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有心想長做 點知下個月工都無得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前排仲要入駿洋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n利申：因濕鳩肺炎而就嚟做唔住嘅航空公司員工<br />\n<br />\n我真係好撚鐘意我份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687989b0e5dfa38339d0c95fc2135764bd75031f","tid":2216070,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:58:41.000Z","msg":"WFH<br />\n<br />\n日日無聊炒股<br />\n<br />\n日頭既時候係HSI<br />\n<br />\n夜晚既時候係DJI<br />\n<br />\n好大壓力"}]}